        "description": "Beam diameter for precise surface prep on TiC; smaller (50-100 μm) for fine details, larger (200-500 μm) for broad areas. 200 μm optimal for uniform cleaning without excessive overlap heating. Source: Equipment specs from Coherent and Trumpf laser systems for industrial cleaning."
